OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782463702
OL,3,C'High casualties' probable, as
OL,4,Cpowerful earthquakes hit Venezuela
OL,6,FTwo powerful earthquakes struck off
OL,7,Fthe coast of Venezuela on Wednesday
OL,8,Fevening, causing widespread damage and
OL,9,Fcollapsing buildings.
OL,11,FThe 7.2 and 7.5 magnitude earthquakes
OL,12,Fcaused buildings to be evacuated in
OL,13,Fcities and areas spread as far as
OL,14,FBrazil's Amazon, over 1,000 miles away.
OL,16,FThe U.S. Geological Survey said that
OL,17,F"high casualties" are expected, and
OL,18,Fthat the "disaster is likely
OL,19,Fwidespread."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
