OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782463702
OL,3,C'High casualties' probable, as
OL,4,Cpowerful earthquakes hit Venezuela
OL,6,FActing President, Delcy Rodriguez,
OL,7,Fsaid the earthquakes caused damage in
OL,8,Fseveral states, but she did not give
OL,9,Fany figures of homes and buildings
OL,10,Fdamaged, injures or fatalities.
OL,12,F"We urge our population to remain
OL,13,Fcalm," Rodriguez said. "We urge unity."
OL,15,FShe also asked all health care
OL,16,Fprofessionals in the country to report
OL,17,Fto hospitals to assist anyone who was
OL,18,Finjured.
OL,20,FThe quakes struck shortly after 6 p.m.
