OL,3,C'High casualties' probable, as
OL,4,Cpowerful earthquakes hit Venezuela
OL,6,FPeople evacuated buildings in the
OL,7,Fcapital Caracas, where parts of the
OL,8,Fcity lost power and phone signal.
OL,10,FCollapsed buildings, toppled
OL,11,Felectricity poles and debris blocked
OL,12,Fstreets.
OL,14,FDonald Trump said in a post on social
OL,15,Fmedia, "the two major earthquakes that
OL,16,Fjust hit the great people of Venezuela
OL,17,Fare both massive in scale and have
OL,18,Fleft a devastating number of deaths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
