OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782463702
OL,3,C'High casualties' probable, as
OL,4,Cpowerful earthquakes hit Venezuela
OL,6,F"The U.S.A. stands ready, willing, and
OL,7,Fable to help!" he added, "early
OL,8,Freports are not good!!!"
OL,10,FCaracas resident Roberto Gamas said,
OL,11,F"The building really shook from side
OL,12,Fto side. Unreal. The force was
OL,13,Fincredibly strong,
OL,15,F"We were walking and it was tossing us
OL,16,Faround. Everything in the apartment
OL,17,Ffell. Well, thank God we were able to
OL,18,Fget out."
OL,26,@sD@AOUzD@IO]
