OL,3,C'High casualties' probable, as
OL,4,Cpowerful earthquakes hit Venezuela
OL,6,FThe earthquakes also damaged the
OL,7,Fcountry's main airport, Simon Bolivar
OL,8,FInternational Airport, which is now
OL,9,Fclosed.
OL,11,FThe USGS said the epicenter of the
OL,12,Ffirst quake was west of the community
OL,13,Fof Moron, located along the country's
OL,14,FCaribbean coast, about 104 miles west
OL,15,Fof Caracas. The quake had a depth of
OL,16,F22 kilometers.
OL,26,@oD@\rwoD@brtuD@Grw
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
