OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782463702
OL,3,C'High casualties' probable, as
OL,4,Cpowerful earthquakes hit Venezuela
OL,6,FThe USGS reported an even larger 7.5-
OL,7,Fmagnitude earthquake just a minute
OL,8,Flater. The second quake had a depth of
OL,9,F10 kilometers and its epicenter was 16
OL,10,Fkilometers (10 miles) southwest of
OL,11,FMoron.
OL,13,FInterior Minister Diosdado Cabello
OL,14,Fsaid the quake could be felt in
OL,15,Fseveral states.
OL,26,@sD@Drw
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
