CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782463702
OL,3,C'High casualties' probable, as
OL,4,Cpowerful earthquakes hit Venezuela
OL,6,F"We understand that some people may be
OL,7,Fdesperate, but we are acting according
OL,8,Fto protocols to activate aid and
OL,9,Frescue efforts to help those who need
OL,10,Fit most," Cabello said on state
OL,11,Ftelevision.
OL,13,FHe added, "be very careful with
OL,14,Fchildren and the elderly; call each
OL,15,Fother and check that no one has been
OL,16,Fharmed."
OL,18,FHe also urged people to remain outside
OL,19,Fas aftershocks could further damage
OL,20,Fsome structures.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@IO]uD@KOUxD@HO]
